for Negro removal!

01:22:07.278 --> 01:22:08.445
Yeah!

01:22:08.511 --> 01:22:09.779
And we're not
gonna accept that!

01:22:09.846 --> 01:22:10.914
No!

01:22:10.982 --> 01:22:13.284
Ladies and gentlemen,
Gabby Horowitz!

01:22:17.754 --> 01:22:19.389
What is a city?

01:22:19.456 --> 01:22:21.491
