01:24:01.258 --> 01:24:02.826
- I'll, uh, I'll see if I can.
- Laura, come on!

01:24:04.128 --> 01:24:05.129
Come.

01:24:09.166 --> 01:24:10.267
Hey, hey, hold up.

01:24:10.334 --> 01:24:12.003
