01:25:09.692 --> 01:25:11.828
They are just
all walking around,

01:25:11.895 --> 01:25:13.464
calm as Hindu cows,

01:25:13.531 --> 01:25:14.798
thinking they live
in a democracy,

01:25:14.864 --> 01:25:16.167
so what could happen?

01:25:16.233 --> 01:25:17.435
Are you gonna write
about this or what?

01:25:17.501 --> 01:25:18.735
