01:28:35.466 --> 01:28:37.601
Giant,
faggot munchkin meat!

01:28:37.668 --> 01:28:39.536
Oh. Okay.

01:28:41.472 --> 01:28:42.805
See...

01:28:42.872 --> 01:28:46.176
I was told to go easy,
and I did...

01:28:46.243 --> 01:28:50.080
